The paper discusses the integration of user preferences in multi-objective optimization, which is a topic that falls under the umbrella of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of metaheuristics and mathematical programming also suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and optimization (cs.RO).
